Randy Olson, PhD, is the director of the ABT Framework Narrative Training program (ABTNarrative.com), author of 12 books on communication including, Houston, We Have A Narrative (University of Chicago Press, 2015), and is the 2020 recipient of the John P. McGovern Award for Excellence in Biomedical Communication from the Southwest Chapter of the American Medical Writers Association.  Matthew David (with a background in screenwriting) and Liz Strauss (with a background in advertising) are long time co-instructors for the ABT Narrative Training team.
